<html>

<head>
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOINDEX, NOFOLLOW">
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOARCHIVE">
<title>Auto Transport Estimate</title>

<style>
	p.pagebreak {   page-break-after: always;}
</style>

</head>

<body>
<% IF pnDEPOSIT < 1 AND _EST.STATUS='F' AND !plAGENT %><!--QUICK EST NO DEPOSIT-->
<font style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:11pt;">Hello <%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.SNAME))%>,<br><br>
My name is <%=pcREP%>, from <%=pcCOMPANY%> <%=IIF(EMPTY(pcICC),"","MC-"+pcICC)%>.<BR>I am reaching out to you regarding your inquiry to transport your vehicle.<BR><BR>
Quote: <%=ALLT(_EST.DEPT)+ALLT(_EST.ORDNO)%><BR><br>
<table style="border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11pt;" border="1" cellSpacing="1" cellPadding="0" width="450">
  <tr>
    <td>Pick-up Info:</td>
    <td>Delivery Info:</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.SCITY))+', '+(_EST.SSTATE)%>&nbsp;</td>
    <td><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.RCITY))+', '+(_EST.RSTATE)%>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br>
Please bear in mind, the price below is based on a tentative date for pick-up that we received of <%=_EST.LBOOKDTE%>, the origin and destination, as well 
as supply and demand. We take this into account to provide an accurate rate based on an estimated pick-up of 12 - 72 hours.
<BR><br>
<table style="border-collapse:collapse;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11pt;" border="1" cellSpacing="1" cellPadding="0" width="450">
  <tr>
    <td width="242">Year / Make / Model</td>
    <td width="202">Price</td>
 </tr>
 <%SELECT _INVAUTO
       SCAN %>
  <tr>
    <td width="242"><%=ALLT(YEAR)+' / '+ALLT(MAKE)+' / '+ALLT(MODEL)%>&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="202" align="right">&nbsp;<%=IIF(UPRC=0,'','$'+ALLT(STR(UPRC,8,2)))%></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDSCAN%>
</table>
<br>
<u>Depending on your flexibility we can match any lower rate that is all-inclusive.</u><br><br>
Please contact me, <%=pcREP%>, <%=pcTOLLFREE%> so I can give you a tailored rate based on your requirements.
You may need your vehicle to arrive after or before a certain date, or picked up by a certain time. I really want to make sure 
we take everything into account to provide you with the best competitive and service based rate.<br><br>
Sincerely,<br><br><%=pcREP%><br>*Se Habla Espańol<br><%=pcTOLLFREE%><br><a href="mailto:<%=pcOUREMAIL%>"><%=pcOUREMAIL%></a><br>
<%=pcCOMPANY%> <%=IIF(EMPTY(pcICC),"","MC-"+pcICC)%>
<%=pcADD1%>&nbsp;<%=pcADD2%><br>
<a href="http://www.fidelityautoshipping.com" style="color: #0563C1;">www.fidelityautoshipping.com</a> | 
<a href="http://www.transportemiauto.com" style="color: #0563C1;">www.transportemiauto.com</a> | 
<a href="http://www.canadaautoshipping.net" style="color: #0563C1;">www.canadaautoshipping.net</a><br>
<font size="2">*PLEASE NOTE: Rates are valid for 5 days from initial quotation<br><br>
Email Disclaimer: This email and any files transmitted with it are confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or
entity to whom they are addressed. If you have received this email in error please notify the sender. This message contains 
confidential information and is intended only for the individual(s) named. If you are not the intended recipient you are 
notified that disclosing, copying, distributing or taking any action in reliance on the contents of this information is 
strictly prohibited. Although Fidelity Auto Shipping Co. has taken reasonable precautions to ensure no viruses are present 
in this email, the company cannot accept responsibility for any loss or damage arising from the use of this email or attachments.</font></font>
<%ELSE%>
  <% IF !plAGENT AND _EST.STATUS='F' %>
<table border="0" align="center" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="700">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" align="center"><img border="0" src="https://eagle.hellomoving.com<%=pcIMG%>" width="100%" height="100"></td>
 </tr>
</table>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width="700" align="center">
  <tr>
    <td><br>
<table border="1" align="center" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#000000" width="100%">
  <tr>
   <td width="75%" VALIGN="TOP" align="center" bgcolor="#000000" colspan="2"><b><font style="font-size:17pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#92D050;">
   <%=IIF(_EST.STATUS='F','Auto Transport Estimate','Auto Transport Job Order')%> <%=IIF(plAGENT,' - Carrier Copy','')%></font></b>&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
   <td width="37%" VALIGN="TOP">
<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" width="100%">
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Quote No.:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=ALLT(_EST.DEPT)+ALLT(_EST.ORDNO)%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Transport Date:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(EMPTY(_EST.LBOOKDTE1),_EST.LBOOKDTE,'Between '+DTOC(_EST.LBOOKDTE)+' to '+DTOC(_EST.LBOOKDTE1))%></b></font></td>
  </tr>
  <% IF !EMPTY(_EST.LBOOKTME)%>
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Arrival Window:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=_EST.LBOOKTME%></b></font></td>
  </tr>  
  <%ENDIF%>
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Representative:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(EMPTY(_EST.REP),PROPER(_EST.USER),PROPER(_EST.REP))%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Rep. Email:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><a href="mailto:<%=pcOUREMAIL%>"><%=pcOUREMAIL%></a></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Mileage:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(_CRG.MILES > 0,ALLT(STR(_CRG.MILES))+' miles','')%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
  </tr>   
   <tr>
     <td width="36%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b>Type of Service:</b></font></td>
     <td width="64%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=pcINTLSERV%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
  </tr>  
</table>   
   </td>
   <td width="38%" VALIGN="TOP">
<table border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" width="100%">
   <tr>
     <td width="100%" colspan="2"><font style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=pcCOMPANY%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
<% IF !EMPTY(pcADD1)%>    
   <tr>
     <td width="100%" colspan="2"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=pcADD1%>&nbsp;<%=pcADD2%></b></font></td>
  </tr>
<%ENDIF%>  
   <tr>
     <td width="50%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=pcTOLLFREE%></b></font></td>
     <td width="50%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(!EMPTY(pcFAX),'Fax: '+pcFAX,'')%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
   <tr>
     <td width="50%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(EMPTY(pcICC),"","ICC MC: "+pcICC)%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
     <td width="50%"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><%=IIF(EMPTY(pcDOT),"","US DOT: "+pcDOT)%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>  
<% IF !EMPTY(pcOURWEB)%>
   <tr>
     <td width="100%" colspan="2"><font face="Calibri" size="3"><b><a href="<%=pcOURWEB%>"><%=pcOURWEB%></a></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
<%ENDIF%>   
</table>   
   </td>
 </tr>
  </table>
 <br>   
<table border="1" align="center" width="700" height="100" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#000000">
  <tr>
	<td height="20" bgcolor="#000000" align="center" width="340"><b><font style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#92D050;">Origin</font></b></td>
	<td height="20" bgcolor="#000000" align="center" width="353"><b><font style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#92D050;">Destination</font></b></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
	<td valign="top" width="340">
<table border="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3">
  <tr>
   <td colspan="2" align="center" width="100%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.SNAME))%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.SLEVEL)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Location:</font></td>
   <td width="131%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.SLEVEL)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>  
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.SADD1) OR !EMPTY(_EST.SADD2)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Address:</font></td>
   <td width="131%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.SADD1)%>&nbsp;<%=ALLT(_EST.SADD2)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
  <tr>
   <td width="30%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">City, State, Zip:</font></td>
   <td width="70%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.SCITY))+', '+(_EST.SSTATE)%>
   &nbsp;<%=ALLT(_EST.SZIP)%><%=IIF(EMPTY(_EST.SCOUNTRY),' ','&nbsp;'+ALLT(_EST.SCOUNTRY))%></font></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Phone 1:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.STELH)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.STELO)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Phone 2:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.STELO)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.SFAX)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Fax:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.SFAX)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
</table>
   </td>
    <td valign="top" width="353">
<table border="0" width="100%" height="19" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3">
  <tr>
   <td colspan="2" align="center" width="100%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.RNAME))%>&nbsp;</b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.RLEVEL)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Location:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.RLEVEL)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>   
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.RADD1) OR !EMPTY(_EST.RADD2)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Address:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.RADD1)%>&nbsp;<%=ALLT(_EST.RADD2)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
  <tr>
   <td width="29%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">City, State, Zip:</font></td>
   <td width="71%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(PROPER(_EST.RCITY))+', '+(_EST.RSTATE)%>
   &nbsp;<%=ALLT(_EST.RZIP)%><%=IIF(EMPTY(_EST.RCOUNTRY),' ','&nbsp;'+ALLT(_EST.RCOUNTRY))%></font></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Phone 1:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.RTELH)%></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%IF !EMPTY(_EST.RTELO)%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Phone 2:</font></td>
   <td width="101%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=ALLT(_EST.RTELO)%></font>&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>
  <tr>
   <td width="1%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;">Email:</font></td>
   <td width="102%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><a href="mailto:<%=ALLT(_EST.EMAIL)%>"><%=IIF(EMPTY(_EST.EMAIL),'',ALLT(_EST.EMAIL))%></a></font>&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>  
</table>    
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<%IF !EMPTY(pcEXTSTOP)%>  
    <br>
<table border="1" align="center" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#000000">
  <tr>
    <td width="33%" align="center" bgcolor="#000000"><b><font style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#92D050;">Additional Notes</b></font></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" width="33%"><font face="Calibri" color="#000000" size="2"><%=pcEXTSTOP%></FONT>&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>
</table>
<%ENDIF%>
<%IF plAGENT%>
<BR>    
<table border="1" align="center" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#000000" width="100%">
  <tr>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Carrier</b></font></td>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Company</b></font></td>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Contact</b></font></td>
   <td width="18%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Email</b></font></td>
 </tr>
  <tr>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><b><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=pcAGENT%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><b><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=pcAGCOMPANY%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
   <td width="19%" align="center"><b><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=pcAGCONTACT%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
   <td width="18%" align="center"><b><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><%=pcAGEMAIL%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
 </tr>
</table>
<%ENDIF%>
    <br>
<table border="1" width="100%" align="center" bordercolor="#000000" style="border-collapse: collapse">
  <tr>
   <td align="center" bgcolor="#000000"><b><font style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#92D050;">Vehicles</font></b></td>
 </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>
<table border="1" width="100%" height="1" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#CCCCCC" style="border-collapse: collapse">
  <tr>
    <td width="18%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Year / Make / Model</b></font></td>
    <td width="8%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Type</b></font></td>
    <td width="3%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Run</b></font></td>    
    <td width="5%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Enclosed<br>Svc.</b></font></td>    
    <td width="23%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Remarks</b></font></td>    
    <td width="3%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Qty</b></font></td>
    <td width="8%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Total<br>Price</b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%SELECT _INVAUTO
       SCAN %>
  <tr>
    <td width="18%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(YEAR)+' / '+ALLT(MAKE)+' / '+ALLT(MODEL)%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="8%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=TYPE%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="3%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=IIF(RUN,'Yes',' No')%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>    
    <td width="5%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=IIF(COVER,'Yes',' No')%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>    
    <td width="23%"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(REMARKS)%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>    
    <td width="3%" align="center"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(STR(QTY))%></b></font>&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="8%" align="right">&nbsp;<font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#3548DD4;"><b>
    <%IF plAGENT%><%=IIF(UPRC=0,'','$'+ALLT(STR(UPRC-DEPOSIT,8,2)))%><%ELSE%>
    <%=IIF(UPRC=0,'','$'+ALLT(STR(UPRC,8,2)))%><%ENDIF%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDSCAN%>
<%IF !plAGENT%> 
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.ORIGINAMT > 0 %>
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Terminal Handling - Origin</b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.ORIGINAMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.DESTINAMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Terminal Handling - Destination</b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.DESTINAMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.BOOKINGAMT > 0 AND _EST.STATUS='O'%> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Booking Fee</b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.BOOKINGAMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.OTHERS1AMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS1)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS1AMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.OTHERS2AMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS2)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS2AMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%> 
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.OTHERS3AMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS3)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.OTHERS3AMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr> 
 <%ENDIF%>
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.EXTRA1AMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.EXTRA1)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.EXTRA1AMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr> 
 <%ENDIF%>
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.EXTRA2AMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.EXTRA2)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.EXTRA2AMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr> 
 <%ENDIF%>      
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.INSAMT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.INS)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.INSAMT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr> 
 <%ENDIF%>
 <% IF _AUTOCRG.DISCOUNT > 0 %> 
  <tr>
   <td width="65%" height="19" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#FF0000;"><b><%=ALLT(_AUTOCRG.DISCTXT)%></b></font></td>
   <td width="7%" align="right" height="19"><font size="2" style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#FF0000;"><b><%='-$'+ALLT(STR(_AUTOCRG.DISCOUNT,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ENDIF%>
<%ENDIF%>   
<%IF !plAGENT%>
  <tr>
   <td width="64%" height="19" align="right" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Total:</b></font></td>
   <td width="8%" align="right" height="19"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#548DD4;"><b><%='$'+ALLT(STR(_EST.SUBTOTAL,8,2))%></b></font></td>
 </tr>
 <%ELSE%>
  <tr>
   <td width="64%" height="19" align="right" colspan="6"><font style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri;"><b>Total Charge:</b></font></td>
