	<b>Services Rendered:</b> The customer acknowledges that they are paying <%=lcDEPTABBR%> for a booking, and not a transportation fee. 
	<%=lcDEPTABBR%> provides services to facilitate a booking of reservations for a consideration. <%=lcDEPTABBR%> makes no warranty for the reservation service.<br>
	<b>Refund & Cancellation Policy:</b> To cancel a booking, all requests must be made online via: <a href="https://fidelityautoshipping.com/cancel/" target="_blank">https://fidelityautoshipping.com/cancel/</a>.
	Should Customer cancel order within 24 hours of booking request, <%=lcDEPTABBR%> will refund Customer all monies received minus any fees incurred to <%=lcDEPTABBR%>
	during that time if applicable. All booking requests within the forty-eight (48) contiguous states excluding ocean shipments in effect longer than 24 hours without 
	reservation can be cancelled but are subject to an administrative fee of $80.00. All bookings with reservations regardless of dates will be unable to be cancelled 
	and therefore non-refundable as services have been rendered as outlined in clause number 30. In the event of Customer`s refusal for release of cargo for Carrier 
	will not invalidate the agreement. Should Customer cancel any International and/or Ocean booking request after twenty-four (24) hours of initial booking, 
	order cancellations are subject to an additional administrative fee of 20% of the total invoice as outlined in the payment agreement.</font></td>
